In our work, we defined the specific growth rates as biomass doubling rates to show even better the differences which occur over time. The percentage inhibition of microalgal growth (Iµi) was calculated based on the determined specific growth rates from Eq. (2):2Iμi(%)=μc-μiμc×100\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
